{
  "stem": "25651.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All this mud that was outside, they were building a road just by putting a stone foundation so that you could drive through the camp with cars or-- so they were making these stone foundations.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody came with a crushed hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish-- Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Krankenbau-- Krankenbau, it's-- it's laughable that there was a hospital, because people just came there to die.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an assembly point to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Particularly with the dysentery in the block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the front of the block, on the chimney, they put a white sheet and they started an operation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they washed his hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The man was screaming blue murder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you couldn't help but watch, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- I'd never seen a hospital operation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Mengele walked in and he said, weitermachen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Weithermachen, continue.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he stood somewhere behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was fascinated by this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And suddenly I feel queasy, you know, because the-- the flesh is falling away, and they're picking this bit of finger and that bit of finger.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I feel a bit queasy, and I collapse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I come to, something is holding me by the scuffle of the neck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a white glove is waving a bottle of ammonia in front of my face.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I sort of squirm away, you know, to try and get away from this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this voice says, [GERMAN] You know, you just watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You'll get used to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was Mengele who was holding me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In order to deal with prisoners, he always wore these white gloves, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "After he handled me, he took the white gloves off, put them on the chimney.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he does his inspection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, they go and see the dysentery.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
